            },
            "answer_text": "For me? I study harder for next time. Or, because some of our subjects don\u2019t actually go into our overall GPA, I just give up on the subjects I knowI\u2019m weak at, and give more attention to my other subjects. Maybe you could focus on something else, if academics aren\u2019t your forte. Like a hobby, or extracurricular. Also, remember that your grades won\u2019t be very inportant down the road, unless it\u2019s for your last year in high school and your grades are very bad, in which case you might consider repeating the year or really dedicating more time to study for the rest of the school year. ",
