            "answer_text": "I usually get bad grades due to the fact that I tend to procrastinate, give up and sometimes I tend to be lazy. So I have trouble keeping up with my learning and studying. Thus my performance tanked. Sometimes I tend to struggle with learning. The point is, I need to just try my best and have a better work ethic. Last semester didn\u2019t go so well(I basically got mostly C\u2019s with one B and a D). If you\u2019re struggling try to be persistent, if you\u2019re still struggling, then you could ask for help. Sometimes you just have to somehow manage to finish the homework if you struggle. ",
