        {
            "author_info": {
                "name": "Hillary Sibille",
                "href": "/profile/Hillary-Sibille"
            },
            "answer_text": "A2A. I\u2019m not a student, so I don\u2019t get grades. The advice I would give to a student who is earning poor grades is to find out why. Talk to your teacher(s) or a learning specialist. Assess whether you are doing the work correctly and understand the material. Then, figure out whether you are reading for comprehension, retaining information, understanding how to express yourself in writing, etc. In other words, so many steps go into learning and passing tests, and hence, earning grades. Get someone to help you sort out where you\u2019re going wrong so you can start working effectively and competently. I wish you well. ",
